*.txt          text
*.md           text
*.cpp          text
*.h            text
.gitattributes text
.gitignore     text
TheCMakeLists.txtfile is pretty basic:
project(hello)
cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 2.8)
add_executable(hello hello.cpp)
install(TARGETS hello DESTINATION bin)
Finally, the actualhello.cppfile:
#include <iostream>
int main() {
std::cout << "Hello World!" << std::endl;
return 0;
}